title: The Suicide Squad Game Did WHAT to Batman?!
description:
The new Suicide Squad game launched with the idea of having our plucky squad of villains kill our beloved heroes who've been turned. However, among a sea of other controversies - one stood out among the rest: the mean hostile spirit the creators had towards these iconic heroes.
